00:10:34.580 --> 00:10:35.680 align:middle line:90%
>> Why not?

00:10:35.680 --> 00:10:36.900 align:middle line:90%
>> Because I'm your father.

00:10:36.900 --> 00:10:37.710 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:10:37.710 --> 00:10:42.420 align:middle line:90%
