>> Jesus, Maggie.

00:10:52.860 --> 00:10:54.800 align:middle line:90%
No.

00:10:54.800 --> 00:10:58.060 align:middle line:90%
Have you tried online dating?

00:10:58.060 --> 00:10:59.811 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:10:59.811 --> 00:11:01.760 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh.

