>> The internet is a thriving
community of single people.

00:11:04.250 --> 00:11:06.590 align:middle line:84%
>> Are you excited
about going to college?

00:11:06.590 --> 00:11:08.002 align:middle line:90%
Nervous?

00:11:08.002 --> 00:11:09.050 align:middle line:90%
How about your friends?

00:11:09.050 --> 00:11:14.130 align:middle line:90%


00:11:14.130 --> 00:11:17.080 align:middle line:84%
>> Actually, one of my friends
