out that she's adopted.

00:11:22.363 --> 00:11:23.350 align:middle line:10%
>> Oh, wow.

00:11:23.350 --> 00:11:24.246 align:middle line:10%
Poor girl.

00:11:24.246 --> 00:11:25.644 align:middle line:90%
>> You think?

00:11:25.644 --> 00:11:28.450 align:middle line:90%
>> Well, it's a lot.

00:11:28.450 --> 00:11:31.660 align:middle line:84%
>> Yeah, but she doesn't really
get along with her parents.

00:11:31.660 --> 00:11:33.250 align:middle line:90%
>> Doesn't matter.

00:11:33.250 --> 00:11:34.640 align:middle line:90%
It's a huge thing to deal with.

00:11:34.640 --> 00:11:36.223 align:middle line:84%
>> Yeah, but it could
be a good thing.

00:11:36.223 --> 00:11:45.930 align:middle line:90%


00:11:45.930 --> 00:11:48.416 align:middle line:84%
>> Is this your way of
asking me something?

