>> What?

00:11:49.710 --> 00:11:50.510 align:middle line:90%
No.

00:11:50.510 --> 00:11:50.900 align:middle line:90%
I was just--

00:11:50.900 --> 00:11:52.705 align:middle line:84%
>> I have some bad
news for you, Maggie.

00:11:52.705 --> 00:11:55.320 align:middle line:90%


