You're not adopted.

00:11:56.950 --> 00:11:59.662 align:middle line:90%
I'm the dad you get.

00:11:59.662 --> 00:12:01.520 align:middle line:90%
I know.

00:12:01.520 --> 00:12:02.840 align:middle line:90%
It's disappointing.

00:12:02.840 --> 00:12:05.480 align:middle line:90%


00:12:05.480 --> 00:12:07.160 align:middle line:90%
>> You spoke in hypotheticals?

00:12:07.160 --> 00:12:08.350 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:12:08.350 --> 00:12:09.410 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh no, Mags.

00:12:09.410 --> 00:12:11.840 align:middle line:84%
That is going to make it
so much more difficult when

00:12:11.840 --> 00:12:13.230 align:middle line:90%
you actually have to tell him.

00:12:13.230 --> 00:12:14.210 align:middle line:90%
>> I know.

00:12:14.210 --> 00:12:14.910 align:middle line:90%
>> What are you going to do?

