You're going to
school on Sunday.

00:12:16.285 --> 00:12:19.370 align:middle line:84%
You've got to-- you've got
to wait till Christmas.

00:12:19.370 --> 00:12:21.050 align:middle line:84%
>> We don't even
know these people.

00:12:21.050 --> 00:12:21.350 align:middle line:90%
OK?

00:12:21.350 --> 00:12:23.660 align:middle line:84%
Maybe there's a reason why
Grandma and Grandpa never

00:12:23.660 --> 00:12:26.500 align:middle line:90%
said anything.

00:12:26.500 --> 00:12:29.501 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:12:29.501 --> 00:12:31.500 align:middle line:84%
But don't you think that
should be his decision?

00:12:31.500 --> 00:13:08.680 align:middle line:90%


00:13:08.680 --> 00:13:10.540 align:middle line:90%
>> So you ready?

00:13:10.540 --> 00:13:11.650 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:13:11.650 --> 00:13:13.690 align:middle line:90%
Me and Mom leave in the morning.

00:13:13.690 --> 00:13:15.550 align:middle line:84%
>> Hey, you got that
thing I got you?

00:13:15.550 --> 00:13:17.590 align:middle line:90%
Giants game cup?

00:13:17.590 --> 00:13:19.420 align:middle line:84%
You can put your pens
and pencils in there.

00:13:19.420 --> 00:13:20.220 align:middle line:90%
For your desk.

00:13:20.220 --> 00:13:23.620 align:middle line:84%
>> You know, there just
wasn't any room for it.

00:13:23.620 --> 00:13:25.600 align:middle line:90%
So Dad, I--

00:13:25.600 --> 00:13:26.641 align:middle line:90%
I brought you something.

00:13:26.641 --> 00:13:28.640 align:middle line:84%
>> Are you going to make
good choices at school?

00:13:28.640 --> 00:13:32.280 align:middle line:90%


00:13:32.280 --> 00:13:33.754 align:middle line:90%
>> Sometimes.

00:13:33.754 --> 00:13:35.545 align:middle line:10%
>> Yeah, I know you're
being funny, Maggie,

00:13:35.545 --> 00:13:37.710 align:middle line:10%
but you should
take it seriously.

00:13:37.710 --> 00:13:40.440 align:middle line:84%
>> I promise, I'm
taking it seriously.

00:13:40.440 --> 00:13:41.887 align:middle line:90%
>> I mean really seriously, kid.

00:13:41.887 --> 00:13:42.720 align:middle line:90%
You're an adult now.

00:13:42.720 --> 00:13:43.900 align:middle line:90%
You need to act like it.

00:13:43.900 --> 00:13:44.700 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:13:44.700 --> 00:13:45.630 align:middle line:90%
Dad, I got it.

00:13:45.630 --> 00:13:46.749 align:middle line:90%
I'm a responsible person.

00:13:46.749 --> 00:13:47.790 align:middle line:90%
I'm not a complete idiot.

00:13:47.790 --> 00:13:48.590 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:13:48.590 --> 00:13:50.160 align:middle line:90%
Tell that to my car.

00:13:50.160 --> 00:13:52.978 align:middle line:84%
>> I thought the car
wasn't your concern.

00:13:52.978 --> 00:13:53.830 align:middle line:90%
>> I--

00:13:53.830 --> 00:13:54.630 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah, you did.

00:13:54.630 --> 00:13:54.850 align:middle line:90%
You know what?

00:13:54.850 --> 00:13:57.141 align:middle line:84%
I'll send you a check as soon
as I got a job at school.

00:13:57.141 --> 00:14:01.114 align:middle line:90%


00:14:01.114 --> 00:14:04.200 align:middle line:84%
You know, I came here
to tell you something,

00:14:04.200 --> 00:14:07.042 align:middle line:84%
and I'm going to do it,
despite you being you.

00:14:07.042 --> 00:14:09.000 align:middle line:84%
When I was at Grandpa's
getting his cuff links,

00:14:09.000 --> 00:14:10.260 align:middle line:90%
I found paperwork.

00:14:10.260 --> 00:14:13.653 align:middle line:84%
Government paperwork from
the state of Washington.

00:14:13.653 --> 00:14:15.840 align:middle line:90%
Dad, you were adopted.

00:14:15.840 --> 00:14:18.090 align:middle line:84%
>> If this is another one
of your jokes, I don't get--

00:14:18.090 --> 00:15:12.820 align:middle line:90%


00:15:12.820 --> 00:15:13.660 align:middle line:90%
>> Hello.

00:15:13.660 --> 00:15:14.592 align:middle line:90%
This is William.

00:15:14.592 --> 00:15:17.050 align:middle line:84%
You can leave a message, but
I probably won't listen to it.

00:15:17.050 --> 00:15:19.690 align:middle line:90%
So call back later.

00:15:19.690 --> 00:15:20.726 align:middle line:90%
Press pound.

00:15:20.726 --> 00:15:21.678 align:middle line:90%
[BEEP]

00:15:21.678 --> 00:15:22.630 align:middle line:90%


00:15:22.630 --> 00:15:23.582 align:middle line:90%
>> Hey.

00:15:23.582 --> 00:15:26.621 align:middle line:90%
I-- hi, Dad.

00:15:26.621 --> 00:15:29.550 align:middle line:90%


00:15:29.550 --> 00:15:32.134 align:middle line:90%
It's pretty weird, right?

00:15:32.134 --> 00:15:37.970 align:middle line:84%
I should probably
cancel your phone plan.

00:15:37.970 --> 00:15:39.299 align:middle line:90%
Because you died, Dad.

00:15:39.299 --> 00:15:43.790 align:middle line:90%


00:15:43.790 --> 00:15:46.350 align:middle line:84%
Apparently you didn't tell me
some pretty important stuff

00:15:46.350 --> 00:15:48.820 align:middle line:90%
before that.

00:15:48.820 --> 00:15:53.995 align:middle line:90%
Like what to do with the house.

00:15:53.995 --> 00:15:58.825 align:middle line:90%
Who to do your eulogy.

00:15:58.825 --> 00:16:02.890 align:middle line:84%
Or that I'm not
actually your son.

00:16:02.890 --> 00:16:05.530 align:middle line:84%
You know, I remember
when I was young,

00:16:05.530 --> 00:16:08.410 align:middle line:84%
and you came home every
night, watched the news

00:16:08.410 --> 00:16:10.220 align:middle line:90%
without saying a word to me.

00:16:10.220 --> 00:16:14.550 align:middle line:84%
