watch before going to bed.

00:16:14.550 --> 00:16:19.950 align:middle line:10%
It was like you didn't
know you had a kid.

00:16:19.950 --> 00:16:23.620 align:middle line:84%
Every night I had something
ready to tell you,

00:16:23.620 --> 00:16:24.420 align:middle line:90%
just in case.

00:16:24.420 --> 00:16:27.647 align:middle line:90%


00:16:27.647 --> 00:16:31.420 align:middle line:90%
But you never did, not once.

00:16:31.420 --> 00:16:33.950 align:middle line:90%
You never asked me anything.

00:16:33.950 --> 00:16:35.480 align:middle line:90%
You never talked to me.

00:16:35.480 --> 00:16:38.766 align:middle line:90%
Showed any interest.

00:16:38.766 --> 00:16:39.566 align:middle line:90%
[INAUDIBLE]

00:16:39.566 --> 00:16:41.054 align:middle line:90%
[SOBBING]

00:16:41.054 --> 00:16:48.000 align:middle line:90%


00:16:48.000 --> 00:16:50.400 align:middle line:84%
Well, I'll tell you
what though, Dad.

00:16:50.400 --> 00:16:53.788 align:middle line:90%
I'm not so great at it either.

00:16:53.788 --> 00:16:55.780 align:middle line:90%
The talking and sharing.

00:16:55.780 --> 00:16:58.910 align:middle line:90%


00:16:58.910 --> 00:17:00.520 align:middle line:84%
I couldn't even talk
to you until you

00:17:00.520 --> 00:17:04.157 align:middle line:90%
couldn't respond anymore.

00:17:04.157 --> 00:17:05.490 align:middle line:90%
Which is kind of funny, I guess.

00:17:05.490 --> 00:17:13.260 align:middle line:90%


00:17:13.260 --> 00:17:14.891 align:middle line:90%
I'm not a very good dad.

00:17:14.891 --> 00:17:17.597 align:middle line:90%


00:17:17.597 --> 00:17:20.079 align:middle line:84%
But I'm going to
try to be better.

00:17:20.079 --> 00:17:22.791 align:middle line:90%


00:17:22.791 --> 00:17:24.642 align:middle line:10%
I have to be better.

00:17:24.642 --> 00:17:30.306 align:middle line:90%


00:17:30.306 --> 00:17:32.770 align:middle line:90%
I know you tried too, Dad.

00:17:32.770 --> 00:17:34.686 align:middle line:90%
You did your best.

00:17:34.686 --> 00:17:40.434 align:middle line:90%


00:17:40.434 --> 00:17:43.640 align:middle line:90%
I love you.

00:17:43.640 --> 00:17:45.495 align:middle line:90%
You know that, right?

00:17:45.495 --> 00:17:46.470 align:middle line:90%
>> I know that.

00:17:46.470 --> 00:17:59.916 align:middle line:90%


00:17:59.916 --> 00:18:00.912 align:middle line:90%
>> Bye.

